Infra as code

Rather than config device itself on CLI, deploy config automatically via scripts

Integrate dev and ops efforts

One central repo that determines what is right

Any changes have to be approved from the central repo


CICD Pipeline

Source->Build->Test->Production

Continuous integration means all devs commit changes to the same place

Use VIRL to spin up simulated environment

Use pyATS to test this environment

NetDevOps!
